classification, almost to the end

00:40:39.200 --> 00:40:45.880
of the Naturalization era
in 1952, were significant.

00:40:45.880 --> 00:40:54.970
In 1952, the Immigration and
Naturalization Act was passed,

00:40:54.970 --> 00:40:59.520
